    <p>
        EO.EditableLabel can be used in place of a standard Label control to enable in place
        edit. Key features include:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li>Supports all popular browsers: IE 6.0+, FireFox 1.0+, Mozilla 1.3+, Opera 7.2+,
            Safari 1.3+ and Chrome; </li>
        <li>Ideal for in place editing of short text information such as article title, email
            subject or product description; </li>
        <li>Default style can be used out of box, also fully customizable to fit your site style;
        </li>
        <li>Optional hint text when the Label is empty; </li>
        <li>Custom display format to format the display contents on the client side; </li>
        <li>Support ASP.NET Validators; </li>
    </ul>
</asp:Content>
